  <div id="text-content_C0D14D40-22F6-0135-4AE7-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can add people to an existing thread in the Inbox. </p>
<p>If your recipient list contains more than 100 users, your message will automatically be sent as individual messages to each user.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: When adding users to an existing conversation, you cannot change the course or the subject line.</p>
  </div>
</div>

