  <div id="text-content_C0D2EB50-22F6-0135-4AE9-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Inbox</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_conversation" data-step-uuid="69ea0b8c-7af9-4a80-a5b2-7b11d19078f2">
