  <div id="text-content_C0D57440-22F6-0135-4AF7-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The link will update the total number of people involved in the conversation. </p>
<p>Newly added participants will be able to read and comment on the entire conversation, even the messages that were posted before they were added.</p>
